You can install and type the code in terminal of your code editore to access node-modules for the project.
    Codes- 
I: Run cmds - 
	1. npm install -D tailwindcss
	2. npx tailwindcss init
II: Add * in content
III: Add script in package_json -
		"script":
			"start":"vite"
IV:RUN - npm i vite
V: Create main.css and add - 
			@tailwind base;
			@tailwind components;
			@tailwind utilities;
